{"tid":1391434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有網民準備左一封信比國際警察協會（IPA）","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:42:56.000Z","uid":67347,"like":113,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3db53dac0cf81ba4c615616995c975e0814a8f9c","tid":1391434,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"呢排黑警既所為大家都好不恥<br />\n唯有推佢上國際<br />\n麻煩支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/bhKccTdWM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FbhKccTdWM4&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=87d99957\" target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/bhKccTdWM4</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n<br />\nWith the letter detailing HKPF's excessive violence and showcasing the evidence, we would like to plead with IPA to take the following actions:<br />\n1. Condemn HKPF for its excessive violence, damaging the reputation of police worldwide who adhere to the principle of protecting their citizens.<br />\n2. Re-examine and consider suspending HKPF&rsquo;s membership.<br />\n3. Advise HKPF to restrain from violating the UN Human Rights Standards and Practice for the Police in future protests.<br />\n4. Support the setting up of an independent committee to investigate police brutality and misconduct in this series of unfortunate events."},{"pid":"5dc14d2dcc26c4e5ebb9e64679d036ee8445b6af","tid":1391434,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手推"},{"pid":"d562a55e5659d44c839c7ec07f285b96ae9a0e8a","tid":1391434,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"8月5日大罷工"},{"pid":"7b39c1e805f34f9b16852d4ad7db2a1b80f4647c","tid":1391434,"uid":67347